<div class="top-all">
  <div class="demo-card-wide mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp top-mdl-card">
    <div class="mdl-card__title flash_card_top"></div>
    <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text top-comment">
      自分のフラッシュカードで学習できます<br>
      発音の採点機能・再生機能があります
    </div>
    <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
      <% if current_user.card_files.present? %>
        <%= link_to 'FlashCard',card_file_path(@card),class:"top_button mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-button--colored" %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to 'FlashCard',import_path,class:"top_button mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-button--colored" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="demo-card-wide mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp top-mdl-card">
    <div class="mdl-card__title export_top"></div>
    <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text top-comment">
      自分でオリジナルのフラッシュカードを作ることができます
    </div>

    <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
      <%= link_to 'Export',new_card_file_path,class:"top_button mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-button--colored" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="demo-card-wide mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp top-mdl-card">
    <div class="mdl-card__title edit_top"></div>
    <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text top-comment">
      自分のフラッシュカードを編集・削除することができます
    </div>
    <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
      <%= link_to 'Edit',card_files_path,class:"top_button mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-button--colored" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="demo-card-wide mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp top-mdl-card">
    <div class="mdl-card__title share_top"></div>
    <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text top-comment">
      フラッシュカードを公開したり<br>
      ダウンロードすることができます
    </div>
    <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
      <%= link_to 'Share',"",:method => :post,class:"top_button mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-button--colored" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="demo-card-wide mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp top-mdl-card">
    <div class="mdl-card__title sign_up_top"></div>
    <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text top-comment">
      アカウントを作成します<br>
    </div>
    <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
      <%= link_to 'SignUp',new_user_registration_path,class:"top_button mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-button--colored" %>
    </div>
  </div>
